This package provides:
- Tie::Hash::CustomStorage
- Tie::Array::CustomStorage

Tie::Hash::CustomStorage is a tied hash class which makes it easy to
also specify a custom storage for the hash.

In other words you can get:
- a tied hash of tied scalar
- a tied hash of object 
- a tied hash of value with automatic initialization

Likewise, Tie::Array::CustomStorage is a tied array class where you
can specify the same kind of storage.


